CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774717866
OL,3,C'No evidence' of family voting in by-
OL,4,Celection
OL,6,FThere was "no evidence of any intent
OL,7,Fto influence or refrain any person
OL,8,Ffrom voting" in alleged "family
OL,9,Fvoting" in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,10,Felection, police have concluded.
OL,12,FReform UK raised the allegations after
OL,13,Felection observer group Democracy
OL,14,FVolunteers warned it had witnessed
OL,15,F"concerningly high levels" of the
OL,16,Fillegal practice where two voters use
OL,17,Fone polling booth and potentially
OL,18,Fdirect each other on voting.
OL,26,@nD@KOUpD@LO]wD@AOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774717866
OL,3,C'No evidence' of family voting in by-
OL,4,Celection
OL,6,FNigel Farage's party, whose candidate
OL,7,FMatt Goodwin came second with 28.7% of
OL,8,Fthe vote, reported this to Greater
OL,9,FManchester Police (GMP).
OL,11,FThe Green Party' Hannah Spencer won
OL,12,Fthe by-election in February with 40.7%
OL,13,Fof the vote and a majority of 4,402
OL,15,FIn a statement on Friday, GMP said
OL,16,Feyewitness accounts from observers had
OL,17,Fsuggested some instances of more than
OL,18,Fone person going into a booth at the
OL,19,Fsame time, and of people looking over
OL,20,Fthe shoulder of voters.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774717866
OL,3,C'No evidence' of family voting in by-
OL,4,Celection
OL,6,FBut the force said the observers did
OL,7,Fnot allege "any verbal instruction or
OL,8,Fphysical conduct that indicated one
OL,9,Fperson was directing or coercing
OL,10,Fanother regarding how to vote".
OL,12,F"This is a crucial part of the
OL,13,Flegislation to prove such an offence
OL,14,Fwas committed," it said.
OL,16,FPolice said they had asked Democracy
OL,17,FVolunteers for descriptions of those
OL,18,Falleged to be involved, and timings on
OL,19,Fwhen incidents are believed to have
OL,20,Foccurred.
OL,26,@oD@LOUrD@^O]tD@AOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774717866
OL,3,C'No evidence' of family voting in by-
OL,4,Celection
OL,6,FThese details were not documented, and
OL,7,Fofficers were not provided with any
OL,8,Fidentities or descriptions to pursue,
OL,9,Fmeaning there is "no remaining
OL,10,Freasonable line of inquiry", GMP said.
OL,12,FThe force said it had obtained some
OL,13,FCCTV footage from three polling
OL,14,Fstations visited by Democracy
OL,15,FVolunteers and spoken to the presiding
OL,16,Fofficer from each one, but that no
OL,17,Fevidence was found of direction or
OL,18,Fcoercion.
OL,26,@qD@ROUrD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774717866
OL,3,C'No evidence' of family voting in by-
OL,4,Celection
OL,6,F"There is no evidence to suggest any
OL,7,Fintent to influence or refrain a
OL,8,Fperson from voting as stated in the
OL,9,FBallot Secrecy Act 2023," it said.
OL,11,FNigel Farage has hit out at Greater
OL,12,FManchester Police's decision to close
OL,13,Fa probe into so-called family voting
OL,14,Fin the Gorton and Denton by-election.
OL,16,FReform UK reported the practice to the
OL,17,Fpolice after concerns were raised by a
OL,18,Fgroup of independent election
OL,19,Fobservers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774717866
OL,3,C'No evidence' of family voting in by-
OL,4,Celection
OL,6,FReform leader Mr Farage said:
OL,7,F"Frankly, this is exactly the kind of
OL,8,Festablishment whitewash people are
OL,9,Fsick to death of.
OL,11,F"This isn't good enough. We need
OL,12,Fproper oversight, real accountability
OL,13,Fand the courage to admit when
OL,14,Fsomething isn't right, not another
OL,15,Fbrushed-under-the-carpet report from
OL,16,Fthe usual suspects."
OL,18,FTom Stannard, Returning Officer for
OL,19,Fthe Gorton and Denton By-election,
OL,20,Fsaid he welcomed the conclusions of
OL,21,Fthe police.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774717866
OL,3,C'No evidence' of family voting in by-
OL,4,Celection
OL,6,F"Our elections team have scrutinised
OL,7,Fthe details of observers' claims,
OL,8,Fcross-referencing them against our
OL,9,Frecords from individual polling
OL,10,Fstations.
OL,12,F"The upshot of this examination is
OL,13,Fthat we are confident that the
OL,14,Fallegations are not substantiated, and
OL,15,Fthat the integrity of the by-election
OL,16,Fwas not affected. This is supported by
OL,17,Fthe findings of GMP's investigation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774717866
OL,3,C'No evidence' of family voting in by-
OL,4,Celection
OL,6,F"We reiterate that all of our polling
OL,7,Fstation staff are comprehensively
OL,8,Ftrained to look out for any signs of
OL,9,Fundue influence on voters and can, and
OL,10,Fdo, intervene wherever necessary."
OL,12,FThe Electoral Commission said it would
OL,13,Fspeak to Democracy Volunteers about
OL,14,Fthe observer group's definitions and
OL,15,Ftraining after police found no
OL,16,Fevidence of "family voting" in the
OL,17,FGorton and Denton by-election.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@MOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774717866
OL,3,C'No evidence' of family voting in by-
OL,4,Celection
OL,6,FVijay Rangarajan, chief executive of
OL,7,Fthe Electoral Commission, said:
OL,8,F"Public trust in elections is
OL,9,Fessential.
OL,11,F"We take allegations of fraud or about
OL,12,Fhow polls are conducted very seriously
OL,13,Fand we are grateful that Greater
OL,14,FManchester Police have properly
OL,15,Finvestigated to establish the facts.
OL,16,FVoters must be able to trust that our
OL,17,Felections are secure and conducted
OL,18,Fwith integrity.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774717866
OL,3,C'No evidence' of family voting in by-
OL,4,Celection
OL,6,F"It is equally important that any
OL,7,Fallegations about the security and
OL,8,Fintegrity of elections are supported
OL,9,Fby evidence, so voters have accurate
OL,10,Finformation about how polls are
OL,11,Fconducted.
OL,13,F"GMP have found no evidence of any
OL,14,Fintent to influence or refrain any
OL,15,Fperson from voting. We will discuss
OL,16,Fwith Democracy Volunteers the
OL,17,Fdefinitions they use and the training
OL,18,Fthey give their observers."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
