PN,39911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774717866
OL,3,C'No evidence' of family voting in by-
OL,4,Celection
OL,6,FHe added that polling station staff
OL,7,Fwere "trained to intervene where
OL,8,Fnecessary to protect the secrecy of
OL,9,Fthe ballot ` and did so during this by-
OL,10,Felection".
OL,26,@oD@FOUrD@IO]
